    =======================
    wishbone.encode.msgpack
    =======================

    Version: 1.0.0

    Converts Python dict data structures to MSGPack format.
    -------------------------------------------------------


        Parameters:

            - complete(bool)(False)
               |  When True encodes the complete event.  If False only
               |  encodes the data part.

        Queues:

            - inbox
               |  Incoming messages

            - outbox
               |  Outgoing messges
